{{Dialogue Start}}
;(First interaction)
::<!--Trigger PerformanceE 502027101: Config/Level/NPCDialogue/P10202/F10202001_G43/Act/Act_502027101.json-->
::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_502027101-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502027101-->
::'''Qingzu:''' (Trailblazer), I've heard so much about you but never had the chance to chat with you. May I ask, how can we help you today at the Seat of Divine Foresight?
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Oh nothing, I'm just strolling about.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502027103-->
:::'''Qingzu:''' The Seat of Divine Foresight deals with high-level military secrets. It's really not the kind of place where you could just take a stroll.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} I'd like to learn more about the Seat of Divine Foresight's work...
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502027105-->
:::'''Qingzu:''' I have to warn you, travelers' making inquiries into military secrets is generally known as "espionage."
::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_502027106-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502027106-->
::'''Qingzu:''' If you've really got nothing better to do, I think the Petrichor Inn is looking for cleaners... I know the proprietress there and can introduce you. It might just help you shake the stereotype of being a lazybones.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} You've got an attitude issue.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502027108-->
:::'''Qingzu:''' Sorry, I've been dealing with military affairs and wars for so many centuries that I don't really get a chance to communicate with idlers like yourself. I'm sorry for offending you.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} I think working at the Seat of Divine Foresight would really suit me.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502027110-->
:::'''Qingzu:''' I'm sorry, you must be mistaken. My job description isn't actually "chatting with an idler and helping them kill time."
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Could you please write me a letter of recommendation?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502027112-->
:::'''Qingzu:''' Sorry, I just got notified that the Inn doesn't just hire any idlers for cleaners. I was too rash and nearly put you in a very difficult situation. Please forgive me.
::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_502027113-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502027113-->
::'''Qingzu:''' *sigh* ...Alright, fine. I'll let up on you. You're one of Jing Yuan's guests, after all. My name's Qingzu, and I'm a counselor here at the Seat of Divine Foresight.
::'''Qingzu:''' Come find me if you've ever got any important matters to discuss.
::<!--Ends the current performance-->
::<!--Custom String Trigger: 404021801_Finish-->
;(Subsequent interactions)
::<!--Trigger PerformanceE 502027102: Config/Level/NPCDialogue/P10202/F10202001_G43/Act/Act_502027102.json-->
::'''Qingzu:''' (Trailblazer), may I ask to what do we owe the pleasure of your visit at the Seat of Divine Foresight today?
::<!--Ends the current performance-->
:<!--Open NPC Menu-->
;(If {{cx}}<!--SubMission Started: 404024202-->)
:{{DIcon|?}} I've destroyed the dangerous parcel.
::<!--Trigger PerformanceE 404024203: Config/Level/Mission/4040242/Act/Act404024203.json-->
::'''Qingzu:''' Oh, really?
::'''Qingzu:''' Okay, thanks for letting me know. I will relay the message to the Ten-Lords Commission, and thank you for your support for the Seat of Divine Foresight's cause.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} No need to thank me. It's the least I can do.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_404032064-->
:::'''Qingzu:''' I knew you would say that. You're such a nice person.
:::'''Qingzu:''' With that said, to commend your bravery, I personally prepared a generous reward for you.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Where's my reward?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_404032067-->
:::'''Qingzu:''' Reward? Oh, I almost forgot.
::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_404032068-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_404032068-->
::'''Qingzu:''' Here you go, take it. Don't be polite. It's the least I could do.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Thank you, Qingzu.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_404032070-->
:::'''Qingzu:''' You're welcome, (Trailblazer).
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} I feel like you're just humoring me.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_404032072-->
:::'''Qingzu:''' Humoring? Haha, how could I?
:::'''Qingzu:''' You must be overthinking it. Look at the reward I gave you.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Does that parcel really contain a bomb?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_404032075-->
:::'''Qingzu:''' I don't know. Didn't you destroy the bomb yourself?
:::'''Qingzu:''' If you're really curious, you can always get it back and open it to have a look &mdash; no need to tell me this time.
::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_404032077-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_404032077-->
::'''Qingzu:''' Alright, I have some more work to complete, so I shall take my leave. Once again, thank you for your contributions to the Xianzhou Luofu!
::<!--Ends the current performance-->
::<!--Custom String Trigger: Talk_404024202-->
;(If {{cx}}<!--SubMission Started: 404024203--> and {{cx}}<!--SubMission Started: 404024205--> and {{cx}}<!--SubMission Started: 404024202-->)
:{{DIcon|?}} Jing Yuan told me to give this to you.
::<!--Trigger PerformanceE 404024204: Config/Level/Mission/4040242/Act/Act404024204.json-->
