::'''Qingzu:''' ...
::'''Qingzu:''' Okay, I understand. A mini-neutron bomb, is it? I'll pass it over to the Ten-Lords Commission. Thank you for your support for the Seat of Divine Foresight's cause.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} So my job is over?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_404032083-->
:::'''Qingzu:''' That's all. Just leave the rest to us. You may take your leave...
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} But it felt like it will go off once I leave...
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_404032085-->
