::<!--Trigger PerformanceE 502027107: Config/Level/NPCDialogue/P10202/NPCAct/Act502027107.json-->
::'''Qingzu:''' Without your help, things wouldn't have gone so swimmingly... But, is it truly over?
::'''Qingzu:''' The master diviner acting as the general and my backlog of work show that things aren't over for the Seat of Divine Foresight until the very last Disciple of Sanctus Medicus is arrested.
::'''Qingzu:''' It breaks my heart to see Jing Yuan suffering such a serious injury for the Luofu. So, I hope to do my best to present him with a clean Xianzhou Luofu.
::'''Qingzu:''' Anyway, please allow me to say this personally: Thank you very, very much.
::<!--Ends the current performance-->
